{"title":"党的儿子","authors":["韩笑"],"dates":[{"year":1962,"month":8,"day":3}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"党的儿子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"韩笑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党的儿子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你看他多么威严，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像一颗愤怒的炸弹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不爱说也不爱笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一支歌总挂在嘴边！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上岗的时候他在唱："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“团结起来到明天！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"下岗回来又听见："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“英特纳雄耐尔就一定要实现！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连队的控诉大会上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他突然第一个发言；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"倒不完苦水滔滔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战友们热泪飞溅！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他记不清父亲的面孔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只记得不屈的歌声；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他想不起慈母的容颜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却难忘血腥的皮鞭！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他使劲地挥动铁拳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站在红旗下高喊："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是党的儿子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一辈子要横枪作战！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"普通一兵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瞧他长得"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红红的脸蛋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像个大姑娘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"俱乐部里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他又蹦又跳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像个孩子王！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小组会上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听他发言，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像打机关枪！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看他站岗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"横眉怒目"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好似活金刚！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翻他书包"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"装的尽是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保尔、黄继光……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不要以为"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这样的战士"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"平平常常，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大炮一响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪一个胸前"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不挂满奖章！？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李小红"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高中毕业的李小红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拿着笛子进军营，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大伙一看心里笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这准是个特殊的兵！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要说特殊也不假，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这小伙子可真行，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干活像个小老虎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"待人如同亲弟兄！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"射击当上神枪手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"主席著作学得精，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"入伍不到六个月，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五好红花戴前胸！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱连每次开晚会，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"数他的节目受欢迎！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别看一支小横笛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吹得大伙血沸腾！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一曲红军长征歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是他家传的好本领，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"据说当年他父亲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吹笛战胜雪山冷！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今他又吹起来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鼓舞英雄立战功，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命的笛声人人爱呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命的战士代代红！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄营长"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我问带路的通讯兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"营长叫什么名？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他调皮地??眼睛："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大名鼎鼎的杨子荣！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我心中暗暗纳闷："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"会有这样的事情？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小家伙可真机灵："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哼！不信我讲给你听！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他从三下江南，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"讲到临津江东，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把衷心敬爱的人物，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说得来无影去无踪！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"子弹见他让路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌人见他立正，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深夜大闹贼营，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"活捉美军司令！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他讲得真是生动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仿佛身临其境；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我听得也十分入迷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忘了把事实对证！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不觉来到操场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"部队正演习进攻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士像群猛虎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"插上翅膀冲锋！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我正看得发愣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是谁到身边陪同？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊！粗眉大眼络腮胡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多么熟悉的面孔！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我紧握着一双大手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"本想问他贵姓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不料竟脱口而出："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘿！你准是——杨子荣！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他听了哈哈大笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斜一眼低头的通讯兵："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一定是这个小说迷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又向你艺术加工！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他挽着我的臂膀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听漫山遍野的杀声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说：你瞧这些战士，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪一个不是英雄！？"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}